Label: RAB3A
Comment: Rab3A, located in the synaptic vesicle membrane, interacts with RIM ( Rab3A interacting Molecule) and with Doc2. These interactions are beleived to initiate the process of priming which precedes the fuison of the synaptic vesicle with the plasma membrane.
